properties.property: This is the base of ~Mount Ascent~. |Do you want to know how to get to the top?

Alright, listen up. |According to old tales, ~fire sages~ used to live on top of the mountain. |They would not let anyone near the mountain top in order to ~protect their temple~. |However, there's a legend about a certain ~flower~ which the sages used for their practises. |Rumor has it that the flower grows in places of ~extreme heat~. If this is true, it might be the answer.
